                                [mission.jpg]

   The Clerk's Office of the United States Court of Appeals
   for the Tenth Circuit ensures equal justice is served by maintaining
   a timely and accurate docket, effectively managing caseloads and
   court expenses, sharing knowledge of court rules and procedures
   and disseminating information to the court and all the participants
   in the legal process.
     __________________________________________________________________


                                [vision.jpg]

   The Clerk's Office of the United States Court of Appeals for
   the Tenth Circuit will create a challenging and supportive environment.
   We will effectively and efficiently implement advanced automated
   services.
   We want to be recognized for consistently producing a quality product
   and
   delivering an excellent standard of service to the court and the
   people.
